# Implementation Plan - Final Student Dashboard Migration & Bug Fixes

This plan details the final steps to achieve 100% Livewire migration for the student dashboard, addressing the "balance migration" pages, fixing the test conduct logic, and resolving package listing issues.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> -   **Balance Migration**: We will migrate the remaining controller-based pages (`package_manage`, `feedback`, and `test-instructions`) to Livewire 3 components.
> -   **JS Refactor**: The Test Conduct timer will be moved to Alpine.js to minimize external JS as requested.
> -   **Package Visibility**: Free active packages will now be visible in the "Purchased Packages" list.

